title: GAP Women's 3-Pack Crew Socks
features: CLASSIC CREW SOCKS: Made for everyday wear, these socks are practical and comfortable
REINFORCED TOE AND HEEL: Gap crew socks have reinforced toes and heels to keep up with your active lifestyle
NON-SLIP TOP: These women’s socks have ribbing at the top to ensure they don’t roll or slide down and stay perfectly where they should
SOFT AND STRETCHY KNIT: Made from a super soft and stretchy knit, these socks give your feet the extra cushion and support they need
AMERICAN STYLE FOR ALL AGES: Gap champions a uniquely optimistic sense of American style that bridges the gaps between individuals, generations, and cultures
description: These Gap crew socks for women sit just above the ankle and have reinforced toes and heels to keep up with your active lifestyle. These classic crew socks are ribbed at the top so they sit close to the ankle and don’t stretch out or slip down while walking.
